reviews.reviewText: These are super cute and love the mini Stanley look. The fit super well on my 30oz Stanley straw. A rad loose on the 40oz straw so that is the only issue I have with them. Would make a great gift or stocking stuffer too.

Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I mean they are straw flags
reviews.reviewText: Ok, so they are little flags for your drinks. I have no idea why I ordered them. They are made well and I suppose are exactly what you are looking for when you need some kind of international party full of drinking through straws. I must have been three sheets to the wind when I got these because I have no use for them. I am giving them a 5 star because they are made well and do exactly what they say. I wish there was a way I could rate my self for buying them in the first place. word to the wise... Don't drink and prime.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My son loves flags from around the world, its a weird but safe hobby I guess. He was super pumped for these straw toppers since its hard to find ones more geared towards boys. They have a great selection, nice colors and I am told they are accurate.Big hit!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super Cute, Fits Great
reviews.reviewText: What can I say? These are cute, fit great, and keep my drink safe when I forget to return to it for hours. I was sitting outside reading a few months ago and found a freaking bug in my water when I opened it later. It must have gone down the straw! You can bet I LEAPT to order these once that was discovered. No more bugs in my water. Instead, I have super cute and useful little straw toppers.
